#. Tag: para
#. +> stable5
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "A mouse gesture can be changed by clicking the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button below the area that displays the mouse gesture, which will open a window. Hold down the &LMB; and draw the desired mouse gesture in the area provided. The gesture will be saved when you release the &LMB;."
msgstr ""

