msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#. +> stable5
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Action</guilabel> tab is where you configure the action that will be performed when the shortcut is triggered. There are several types of actions that have different configuration options:"
